=Description=

"A voucher is an encrypted digital representation which stands for or represents something else. A voucher is said to be "backed" by whatever underlies it, such as gold or silver. Vouchers are digital bearer certificates circulated and validated by a Publisher.


So what is the [[P2P Voucher Payment System]]? It is a mechanism for the secure, anonymous exchange of digital vouchers peer-to-peer between users, implemented as an extension to XMPP (aka Jabber), an instant messaging service. Basically, you can pay anyone you can chat with."
(http://voucher-safe.org/tiki-index.php)

